  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=l54d88unlc]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=l54d88unlc]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=tm6otgbmpr]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=tm6otgbmpr]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=rlodgmje51]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=rlodgmje51]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=mc0lm9s1t8]{color:#3d90b3} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=mc0lm9s1t8]{color:#4c9fc2}[data-colorid=ncbxwiwtfo]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ncbxwiwtfo]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=w7mvnd1w5k]{color:#192e59} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=w7mvnd1w5k]{color:#a6bbe6}[data-colorid=ydby2sy2du]{color:#192e59} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ydby2sy2du]{color:#a6bbe6}[data-colorid=qx059gut49]{color:#192e59} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=qx059gut49]{color:#a6bbe6}[data-colorid=uo4uqcw95s]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=uo4uqcw95s]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=d4udtbgvuj]{color:#192e59} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=d4udtbgvuj]{color:#a6bbe6}[data-colorid=y9c6ifxhtx]{color:#4269b8} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=y9c6ifxhtx]{color:#476ebd}[data-colorid=wceoicw2os]{color:#192e59} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=wceoicw2os]{color:#a6bbe6}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_Smoke.png\" width=\"1407\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1407&amp;height=791\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544647040\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_Smoke.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544647025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"dd51b42d-657a-477a-b6de-4a269c12066b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1920&amp;height=1080 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1407&amp;height=791 1x\" /></span><p /><hr /><h1 id=\"Smoke-Smoke\">Smoke</h1><p><br /><strong><span data-colorid=\"l54d88unlc\">Enable Smoke</span></strong><br />Decides whether the smoke density of volume will render or not. If disabled and the Fire tab is enabled, this operation replaces the density field with the fire volume field specified in the Bindings tab instead of the smoke volume field. If both smoke and fire are disabled then the result defaults to the input volume. This does not affect data generated from Scatter<br /><br /><br /></p><hr /><p><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>If Smoke is disabled and the Fire tab is enabled, this operation replaces the density field with the fire volume field specified in the Bindings tab instead of the smoke volume field.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_NoSmoke_WithFire.png\" width=\"686\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_NoSmoke_WithFire.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_NoSmoke_WithFire.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544647070\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_NoSmoke_WithFire.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544647025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1697fb2b-2dc9-4b11-8aee-7c94c3e61879\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_NoSmoke_WithFire.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1372&amp;height=770 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_NoSmoke_WithFire.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><hr /><p><br /></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>If both smoke and fire are disabled then the result defaults to the input volume as seen in the image above.&nbsp; <br /><em>Note: this does not affect data generated from Scatter</em></p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_Scatter.png\" width=\"686\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_Scatter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_Scatter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544647067\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_Scatter.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544647025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"cbf2a212-9baa-4529-a892-41c91328ffd6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_Scatter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1372&amp;height=770 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_460_Scatter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><p /><hr /><p><br /></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"704\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_PyroHDA_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=704&amp;height=198\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647025/RenderMan_PyroHDA_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"303\" data-width=\"1076\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544647037\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_PyroHDA_Smoke.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544647025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"64e1c180-e930-44fa-acbb-273c8092502f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_PyroHDA_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1076&amp;height=303 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_PyroHDA_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=704&amp;height=198 1x\" /></span><p><br /><strong><span data-colorid=\"tm6otgbmpr\">Density Scale</span></strong><br /><span data-colorid=\"qx059gut49\">Multiplies the density of the smoke volume by this value. Thicker density can produce darker colors and more opaque shadows in renders.</span></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"align-start\" data-local-id=\"15ff7290-0502-440b-991f-0cdf40604968\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Pyro_f24_20Den_Smoke.png\" width=\"335\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_20Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=335&amp;height=188\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_20Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544647064\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Pyro_f24_20Den_Smoke.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544647025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c5006993-5350-4755-9570-a5e51e4c0a41\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_20Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=670&amp;height=376 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_20Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=335&amp;height=188 1x\" /></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Pyro_f24_50Den_Smoke.png\" width=\"335\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_50Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162468&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=335&amp;height=188\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_50Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162468&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544647055\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Pyro_f24_50Den_Smoke.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544647025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ac575eae-3a68-4d35-885a-3747c8899faa\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_50Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162468&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=670&amp;height=376 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_50Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162468&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=335&amp;height=188 1x\" /></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Pyro_f24_100Den_Smoke.png\" width=\"335\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_100Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162469&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=335&amp;height=188\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_100Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162469&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544647061\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Pyro_f24_100Den_Smoke.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544647025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"303bdeef-5c94-43bf-920b-751e35f2a5f1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_100Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162469&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=670&amp;height=376 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_100Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162469&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=335&amp;height=188 1x\" /></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderMan_Pyro_f24_200Den_Smoke.png\" width=\"335\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_200Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162469&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=335&amp;height=188\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_200Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162469&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544647058\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Pyro_f24_200Den_Smoke.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544647025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"b8d5c80b-53f1-4c19-a4fc-223ccebf2418\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_200Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162469&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=670&amp;height=376 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/RenderMan_Pyro_f24_200Den_Smoke.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162469&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=335&amp;height=188 1x\" /></span></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><span data-colorid=\"mc0lm9s1t8\">The above images demonstrate Smoke Density values of 20 / 50 / 100 / 200</span><br /><br /></p><p /><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"uo4uqcw95s\">Density Ramp</span></strong><br /><span data-colorid=\"d4udtbgvuj\">Ramp for remapping source values of the density volume. This is used in conjunction with the Density Scale when 'Use Ramp' is enabled for editing instead of 'Constant.'</span></p><p><br /></p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"y9c6ifxhtx\">Density Source Range for Remapped Smoke Density</span></strong><br /><span data-colorid=\"wceoicw2os\">A fit operation that fits these source values to 0-1 for accurate remapping using the ramp. Values outside of this range are clamped.</span></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"12560874-03a1-440c-b7bc-0d8fa181efdd\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p><strong>Pro Tip:</strong><br />Using the Ramped Smoke Density can be used to sharpen the look of your volume by remapping the left side of the ramp to zero to remove very low densities.&nbsp;</p></div></div><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><hr /><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"ncbxwiwtfo\">Smoke Color</span></strong><br /></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Defines the color of the smoke, either with a constant color or via a ramp.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Smoke1.png\" width=\"686\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/Smoke1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647025/Smoke1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544647052\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Smoke1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544647025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"685ce8a7-f7ca-47e0-8e0a-1f10008b8e4e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/Smoke1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1372&amp;height=770 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/Smoke1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385 1x\" /></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Smoke1 Settings.png\" width=\"686\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/Smoke1%20Settings.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=193\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647025/Smoke1%20Settings.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"303\" data-width=\"1076\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544647049\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Smoke1 Settings.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544647025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"22ea8a31-f339-44f8-be93-52ab8ff18cdf\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/Smoke1%20Settings.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1076&amp;height=303 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/Smoke1%20Settings.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=193 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Constant Smoke Color using a simple vector parameter. This applies the same color to all the voxels defined as areas of smoke (Density field - Flame field).</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Smoke2.png\" width=\"686\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/Smoke2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647025/Smoke2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544647046\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Smoke2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544647025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e543709f-13b8-4556-af16-b44376f452a1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/Smoke2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1372&amp;height=770 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/Smoke2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162298&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=385 1x\" /></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Smoke2 Settings.png\" width=\"686\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/Smoke2%20Settings.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=178\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544647025/Smoke2%20Settings.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"277\" data-width=\"1064\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544647043\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Smoke2 Settings.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544647025\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"df0b427c-3ec8-4fbe-8e21-2d145cd6a221\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/Smoke2%20Settings.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1064&amp;height=277 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544647025/Smoke2%20Settings.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433162084&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=686&amp;height=178 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Ramped Smoke Color using the values from Density Range. <span data-colorid=\"ydby2sy2du\">This applies the ramped color to all the voxels defined as areas of smoke (Density field - Flame field).</span></p><p><br /></p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"rlodgmje51\">Density Range for Ramped Smoke Color</span></strong><br /></p><p><span data-colorid=\"w7mvnd1w5k\">A fit operation that fits these source values to 0-1 for accurate mapping on the Smoke Color Ramp. Values outside of this range are clamped and will receive the color on either end of the ramp. If the maximum density of your simulation is 2, for example, then putting 0 in the minimum and 2 in the maximum will provide full, unclamped color coverage of your simulation data.</span></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"f5b4492f-eb88-4808-9b6b-d51967bb3d1a\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p><strong>Pro Tip:</strong><br />Using the Ramped Smoke Color can help improve the depth of your smoke without increasing the density scale for simulations like bonfires or candles. Your simulation density data should have varying values to increase the variation of color using the ramp.</p></div></div><p><br /></p><p><br /></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
  },
